metadata.name: The Modifications of Clouds #1
metadata.description: Cloud symbolism is closely connected to the relationship of feelings and emotions. These feelings or emotions could range from Confidence, Confusion, Burden, Remorse, Satisfaction, and many more. The Modifications of Clouds is a collection of 89 photographs taken over the last 15 years on multiple mediums. These clouds are meant to find you, wherever you are in life, to bring you the feeling or emotion that you are in search of.
